#
# Not in original.
#
# J212: Get field from input line.
#
# This gets the field starting in column
# 1W25 of the input line 1W24, of length 1W30,
# and places it in input string data term (0).
# 1W25 is incremented by 1W30.
#
# Output equals input (0).
#
# Used to implement J181 and J182.
#
# 1 input and output.
#
%J212  11W24
%        J6
%        J121
%      209-3
%      11W30
%      11W25
%      109-1
%        J121
%      109-2
%        J6
%      109-1
%        J111
%      119-3
%      05@157
%      11W30
%      11W25
%      11W25
%        J110  J8
%9-1  +01      0
%9-2  +01      1
%9-3     0     0
